title: Recap of Eli Manning's return on MNF & takeaways from Conference Championship Weekend
itunes:title: Recap of Eli Manning's return on MNF & takeaways from Conference Championship Weekend
description:
Rhett Lewis fills in for DJ and Bucky joins from London for a new episode. First, the guys recap the Eagles win over Eli Manning and the Giants on Monday night (3:45). Next, the duo looks back at conference championship weekend and gives their three biggest takeaways from it (10:25). After, the pair does an early preview of the Peach and Fiesta Bowl (33:15).
